IGitStatus
public class CliGitStatus
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGitStatus

Command-line implementation of the IGitStatus interface. TODO - Need to parse -v option in a better way. Currently GitStatusResponse does not save any output related to -v options such as lines containing diffs, or +++ etc.
